  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed mansard roof extension, by reason of its size, scale, location and detailed design, would result in the loss of the original roof form within a terrace with an unbroken roof line and would result in an overly dominant and obtrusive form of development that fails to respect the character and appearance of the host property and the wider terrace it forms part of.&amp;nbsp; As such, the proposed development is contrary to policies D3 (Optimising Site Capacity through the Design-led Approach) and D4 (Delivering good design) of the London Plan (2021) and policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and LP17 (Housing Design) of the Hackney Local Plan 2033 (2020) and the guidance contained within Hackney Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&lt;/p&gt;"
